


					Html Notes
					**********


1. HTML Structure and save it(.html).
2. Comments in HTML
3. Heading and paragraph in HTML
4. Text formatting in HTML(b,u,i,del,sup,sub,strike)
5. how  to add images in HTML( img tag )
6. how to use an Anchor tag(a tag)
7.  how to use List in HTML (ul, ol )
8. Tables in HTML
9. How to make Form in HTML (TextBox, Password, Radio Button, CheckBox, TextArea, Dropdown Box)

